<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>PlacementBridge | Secure Coordination for Districts and Outside Providers</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="PlacementBridge helps school districts securely coordinate communication, documents, and follow-up tasks with tutors, service providers, and out-of-district placements."
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f8fc;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-soft: #f8fbff;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --line: #dbe6f2;
      --line-soft: #e8eef6;
      --primary: #2563eb;
      --primary-dark: #1d4ed8;
      --primary-soft: #eff6ff;
      --dark: #0f172a;
      --dark-2: #172033;
      --success-bg: #e8f8ee;
      --success-text: #166534;
      --warn-bg: #fff4dd;
      --warn-text: #9a5b00;
      --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      --shadow-soft: 0 10px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
      --radius-xl: 30px;
      --radius-lg: 22px;
      --radius-md: 16px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbff 0%, #eef4fa 100%);
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: rgba(248, 251, 255, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(219, 230, 242, 0.9);
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, #23314b 100%);
      color: #fff;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .brand-text {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
      border-color: var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 64px 0 34px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.08fr 0.92fr;
      gap: 30px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 18px;
      font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 68px);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .hero-proof {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .proof-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .proof-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .proof-value {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .proof-sub {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .panel {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .preview {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .preview-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .preview-heading {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .preview-sub {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .workspace {
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .workspace-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .workspace-name {
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .tag-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .tag.blue {
      background: var(--primary-soft);
      color: var(--primary-dark);
    }

    .tag.warn {
      background: var(--warn-bg);
      color: var(--warn-text);
    }

    .tag.success {
      background: var(--success-bg);
      color: var(--success-text);
    }

    .thread-preview {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .thread-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .thread-card.active {
      border-color: var(--dark);
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .thread-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .thread-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .thread-meta {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: inherit;
      opacity: 0.82;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 36px 0;
    }

    .section-header {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.04;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .section-header p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .icon-box {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: var(--primary-soft);
      color: var(--primary-dark);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .how-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .step-num {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary-dark);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .comm-shell {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 370px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .thread-list,
    .thread-detail {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .thread-list h3,
    .thread-detail h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .thread-list .sub,
    .thread-detail .sub {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .filter-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }

    .chip {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .thread-btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.18s ease;
    }

    .thread-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .thread-btn.active {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--dark);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
    }

    .thread-btn .top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .thread-btn .title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .thread-btn .meta,
    .thread-btn .body {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      opacity: 0.88;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .badge.warn {
      background: var(--warn-bg);
      color: var(--warn-text);
    }

    .badge.success {
      background: var(--success-bg);
      color: var(--success-text);
    }

    .badge.blue {
      background: var(--primary-soft);
      color: var(--primary-dark);
    }

    .detail-header {
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .detail-title {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .detail-meta {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .detail-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .message-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .message {
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .message.dark {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--dark);
    }

    .message-top {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .message-name {
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .message-role {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: #f2f6fb;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .message.dark .message-role {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .message-time {
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.72;
    }

    .message p {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .attachment {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #f2f6fb;
    }

    .message.dark .attachment {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .pricing {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .price-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .price-card.featured {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, var(--dark-2) 100%);
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .price-tier {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      opacity: 0.72;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .price-amount {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .price-card p {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: inherit;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .price-card ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }

    .cta {
      margin: 38px 0 64px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1f2b45 100%);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 34px;
      padding: 34px;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 46px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.16);
    }

    .cta-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.04;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .cta p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .cta-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .cta-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .cta-box p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 0 0 42px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .comm-shell,
      .pricing,
      .how-grid,
      .grid-3,
      .cta-grid,
      .hero-proof {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .topbar-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .nav {
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 44px;
      }

      .panel,
      .thread-list,
      .thread-detail,
      .card,
      .price-card,
      .cta {
        border-radius: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container topbar-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark">PB</div>
        <div class="brand-text">
          <div class="brand-name">PlacementBridge</div>
          <div class="brand-sub">Secure coordination for districts and outside providers</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a>
        <a href="#communication">Communication</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#pilot" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:12px 16px;">Request Demo</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Built for district-to-provider coordination</div>
        <h1>Replace email chaos with one secure collaboration hub.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          PlacementBridge helps school districts securely communicate, share documents, assign follow-ups,
          and track outside-provider coordination in one student-specific workspace.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#pilot" class="btn btn-primary">Request pilot demo</a>
          <a href="#communication" class="btn btn-secondary">See communication workflow</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-proof">
          <div class="proof-card">
            <div class="proof-label">Core promise</div>
            <div class="proof-value">1 hub</div>
            <div class="proof-sub">for communication, files, permissions, and next steps</div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-card">
            <div class="proof-label">Primary buyer</div>
            <div class="proof-value">District</div>
            <div class="proof-sub">special education leadership and coordinators</div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-card">
            <div class="proof-label">Pilot motion</div>
            <div class="proof-value">6 weeks</div>
            <div class="proof-sub">to prove value with a focused initial rollout</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel preview">
        <div class="preview-top">
          <div>
            <h3 class="preview-heading">Inside the student workspace</h3>
            <p class="preview-sub">A cleaner, more controlled workflow than scattered email threads and attachments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="workspace">
          <div class="workspace-header">
            <div class="workspace-name">Student A. Workspace</div>
            <div class="tag-row">
              <div class="tag blue">Active</div>
              <div class="tag warn">Awaiting report</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="thread-preview">
            <div class="thread-card active">
              <div class="thread-top">
                <div>
                  <p class="thread-title">Need weekly behavior summary by Friday</p>
                  <p class="thread-meta">Case Manager · Riverbend Collaborative · 9:12 AM</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tag warn">Awaiting response</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="thread-card">
              <div class="thread-top">
                <div>
                  <p class="thread-title">Tutor update: math fluency improving</p>
                  <p class="thread-meta">Lighthouse Tutoring · Yesterday</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tag blue">Open</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="thread-card">
              <div class="thread-top">
                <div>
                  <p class="thread-title">Counseling session summary added</p>
                  <p class="thread-meta">Thrive Related Services · Mar 7</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tag success">Resolved</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-kicker">Exact MVP</div>
        <h2>Version one stays focused on the operational pain districts actually feel.</h2>
        <p>
          PlacementBridge is not trying to replace an SIS, LMS, or full IEP platform.
          It is built to solve the day-to-day coordination gap between districts and outside providers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-box">👥</div>
          <h3>Student workspaces</h3>
          <p>Each student has one secure coordination room with the appropriate district team and outside partners.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-box">🔐</div>
          <h3>Role-based access</h3>
          <p>District admins, case managers, tutors, and providers only see what they are allowed to access.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-box">💬</div>
          <h3>Secure messaging</h3>
          <p>Conversation threads stay tied to the student workspace instead of disappearing into inboxes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
